from selenium import webdriver
from selenium.webdriver.chrome.service import Service
from selenium.webdriver.chrome.options import Options
from selenium.webdriver.common.by import By
from selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait
from selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions as EC
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import json
import time
import sys

CHROME_DRIVER_PATH = r"C:\Users\kashi\anaconda3\Lib\site-packages\chromedriver_autoinstaller\128\chromedriver.exe"

chrome_options = Options()
chrome_options.add_argument("--headless")
service = Service(CHROME_DRIVER_PATH)
driver = webdriver.Chrome(service=service, options=chrome_options)

def log_data_size(data, label):
    size = sys.getsizeof(data)
    print(f"{label} Data Size: {size} bytes")

def login():
    try:
        driver.get('https://loadboard.doft.com/login')
        username_input = WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, 'driver_email'))
        )
        password_input = WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, 'driver_password'))
        )
        username_input.send_keys('kashifliaqat606@gmail.com')
        password_input.send_keys('Kashif@606')
        login_button = WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.ID, 'submitBtn'))
        )
        login_button.click()

        # Wait for successful login and redirection
        WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.url_changes('https://loadboard.doft.com/login')
        )
        print("Login successful.")
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"An error occurred during login: {e}")
        driver.save_screenshot('login_error.png')  # Save a screenshot for debugging

def extract_live_data_from_user_dashboard_page():
    try:
        driver.get('https://loadboard.doft.com/panel#fid=628816')
        WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, 'dTable_wrapper'))
        )
        time.sleep(10)  # Ensure content has fully loaded

        page_source = driver.page_source
        soup = BeautifulSoup(page_source, 'html.parser')
        data = []
        table_wrapper = soup.find(id='dTable_wrapper')

        if table_wrapper:
            table_rows = table_wrapper.select('.b-load')
            for row in table_rows:
                item = {
                    'id': row.get('data-id'),
                    'uid': row.get('data-uid'),
                    'pickup': row.select_one('.c.c-pu').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-pu') else None,
                    'age': row.select_one('.c.c-age').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-age') else None,
                    'origin': row.select_one('.c.c-addr').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-addr') else None,
                    'destination': row.select_one('.c.c-dest').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-dest') else None,
                    'weight': row.select_one('.c.c-weight').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-weight') else None,
                    'distance': row.select_one('.c.c-dist').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-dist') else None,
                    'price': row.select_one('.c.c-price').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-price') else None,
                    'company': row.select_one('.c.c-company').get_text(strip=True) if row.select_one('.c.c-company') else None,
                    'phone': row.select_one('a.phone-link').get('data-phone-num') if row.select_one('a.phone-link') else None
                }
                data.append(item)

        json_data = json.dumps(data, indent=4)
        print("Dashboard Data:")
        print(json_data)
        log_data_size(json_data, "Dashboard")

    except Exception as e:
        print(f"An error occurred in extract_live_data_from_user_dashboard_page: {e}")
        driver.save_screenshot('dashboard_error.png')  # Save a screenshot for debugging

def extract_live_data_from_main_page():
    try:
        driver.get('https://loadboard.doft.com/')
        WebDriverWait(driver, 30).until(
            EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, 'loadsWrp'))
        )
        page_source = driver.page_source
        soup = BeautifulSoup(page_source, 'html.parser')
        loads_wrapper = soup.find(id='loadsWrp')
        loads_data = []
        if loads_wrapper:
            loads = loads_wrapper.find_all(class_='load')
            for load in loads:
                item = {
                    'pickup': load.find_all('div', class_='col-3 addr')[0].get_text(strip=True),
                    'destination': load.find_all('div', class_='col-3 addr')[1].get_text(strip=True),
                    'date': load.find_all('div', class_='col-2')[0].get_text(strip=True),
                    'weight': load.find_all('div', class_='col-1')[0].get_text(strip=True),
                    'distance': load.find_all('div', class_='col-2')[1].get_text(strip=True),
                    'type': load.find_all('div', class_='col-1')[1].find('span').get_text(strip=True)
                }
                loads_data.append(item)

        json_data = json.dumps(loads_data, indent=4)
        print("Main Page Data:")
        print(json_data)
        log_data_size(json_data, "Main Page")

        driver.get('https://loadboard.doft.com/ajax/get-companies-for-filter')
        time.sleep(5)
        page_source = driver.page_source
        soup = BeautifulSoup(page_source, 'html.parser')
        json_data_ajax = soup.find('body').text
        data_ajax = json.loads(json_data_ajax)
        json_data_ajax = json.dumps(data_ajax, indent=4)
        print("Companies Data:")
        print(json_data_ajax)
        log_data_size(json_data_ajax, "Companies")
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"An error occurred in extract_live_data_from_main_page: {e}")

def main():
    login()  # Perform login once
    while True:
        extract_live_data_from_user_dashboard_page()
        extract_live_data_from_main_page()
        time.sleep(60)  # Refresh every minute to avoid excessive requests

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
